{"tid":998981,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[義氣真姐妹]Lisa捱批評 Jennie保證：她由我們保護！","createTime":"2019-01-28T11:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T10:29:23.000Z","uid":58335,"like":21,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"690514ccb1b2d38544736a91103679af5551b9fc","tid":998981,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T11:19:07.000Z","msg":"Jennie真係一個好女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nJennie：Lisa由我們來保護！<br />\n<br />\nBLACKPINK日前在泰國，亦是Lisa的出生地開演唱會，成員們在台上發表感人的言論，向粉絲保證Lisa會由成員保護好，同時回應了日前有人攻擊Lisa長相的事。<br />\n<br />\n因為Lisa的一個紅地氈裝扮，讓她受盡韓國網友歧視言論的攻擊。一些無理的網友指Lisa卸妝後只是泰國女子，又一直針對Lisa的身材和外貌作出攻擊。泰國有節目播出了有關惡性評論，令泰國的粉絲群認定韓國人歧視泰國人，更發起了「#RespectLisa」運動，引起軒然大波。<br />\n<br />\n對事件一直沉默的BLACKPINK成員，藉12日的泰國場，在台上說出了她們會支持和保護Lisa的説話：「大家應該為Lisa感到驕傲，她很強大、很健康，也很積極」、「我很想在Lisa家鄉說這番話，讓每個人都知道我們會好好照顧Lisa的」。雖然不知道事後網友又會有什麽回應，但相信成員會好好照顧在異鄉奮鬥的Lisa的！<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/01/20190115_EN_LISA_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F01%2F20190115_EN_LISA_1.jpg&h=ea27e60b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/01/20190115_EN_LISA_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F01%2F20190115_EN_LISA_3.jpg&h=a802e176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/3852242-lisa%E5%8F%97%E7%9B%A1%E6%83%A1%E8%A9%95%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A-jennie%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%89%EF%BC%9A%E5%A5%B9%E7%94%B1%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%EF%BC%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F3852242-lisa%25E5